					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Square seems to like detecting resets. In Final Fantasy games, they skip the story intro. In Rad Racer and 3D World Runner they also skip the title screen, and if you're in the ending you can press reset to watch the ending again !
<br />
<br />They do that just by having some particular variable set to particular states, and they check those variables when booting. Note that those games does not clear the memory so this technique works.</div>

					
